patthana7.4:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in MN 4.)
patthana7.4:0.3_0: As he did, he too has lost his throat.
patthana7.4:1.1_0: Neither give rise to perceptions of grasping. ...
patthana7.4:2.1_0: Neither give rise to diversity of perceptions ...
patthana7.4:3.1_0: Neither give rise to diversity of perceptions, and because of grasping.
patthana7.4:4.1_0: twenty-five years of age, foot have gotten by one foot.
